Class GraphQualifierHierarchy

  • java.lang.Object
    • checkers.types.QualifierHierarchy

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FenumChecker.FenumQualifierHierarchy, UnitsChecker.UnitsQualifierHierarchy

    public class GraphQualifierHierarchy
extends MultiGraphQualifierHierarchy
    Represents the type qualifier hierarchy of a type system. This class is immutable and can be only created through GraphFactory.
